@mheon @baude PTAL

Opening to allow early review. I still have to add a tests of course, one thing that is broken is selinux support, the files must be labelled properly so the container is allowed to read them, https://github.com/containers/container-selinux/pull/360. In case someone likes to test locally you can use `--security-opt label=disable` for now to work around it.

cc @mtrmac (in case you are interested how the caller of GetLocalBlobPath() looks)
